name: The 11th Int'l Conference on Computational Intelligence and Software Engineering (CiSE 2019)
content: The 11th Int'l Conference on Computational Intelligence and Software Engineering (CiSE 2019) will be held in Sanya, China during January 3-5, 2019\. This Conference will cover issues on Computational Intelligence and Software Engineering. It dedicates to creating a stage for exchanging the latest research results and sharing the advanced research methods.
